<title>NIGER: Medical staff strike in Niger.</title>
<headline>Medical staff strike in Niger.</headline>
<dateline>NIAMEY 1997-07-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Doctors, nurses and other medical workers in Niger began a 72-hour pay strike on Tuesday, providing only a minimum service in the capital's main hospitals, union sources said.</p>
<p>Medical workers' unions are demanding better housing and other allowances. They staged a three-day strike in June.</p>
